text.text:
In joining Menarini Asia-Pacific, you are entering the dynamic healthcare sector as part of the world’s leading Italian pharmaceutical company, with a 135-year legacy of invigorating lives. As a valued member of our team, we are committed to empowering you with the skills, knowledge and opportunities to advance our mission in Asia Pacific and champion the region’s healthcare needs.

As an equal opportunity employer, we value your abilities above all else. Importantly, we seek out talents who embody the Menarini DNA (link to Living Out Our DNA) and are passionate about making healthier, happier living a reality for all.

From competitive compensation packages to flexible work arrangements and leave options, we have curated a range of benefits that support the well-being of our people.

card_copy.jcr:title: Vision & Value
card_copy.jcr:description: Our values guide our quest to Invigorate Lives across the Asia Pacific.

text.text:
At Menarini Asia-Pacific, we are dedicated to invigorating lives. Driven by a firm belief that good health empowers people to unlock their full potential, we serve over 13 key markets in the region to enhance healthcare and uplift the lives of people and communities.

Menarini Asia-Pacific is a wholly owned subsidiary of the Menarini Group − a leading 140 year old family Italian pharmaceutical company that thrives with the highest level of trust. With its own name to preserve, Menarini today operates in the highest level of compliance and integrity. Uniting the strengths of our global resources with local customer insights, we equip hospitals and healthcare providers with the best medical innovations leveraging its omni-channel marketing and distribution strategy.

Today, armed with strong commercial capabilities and a flexible business and partnering model, we support customers in a diverse range of therapeutic areas by providing access to health and wellness solutions. The agility of our in-country teams allows us to harness synergies across relevant channels and develop customised go-to-market models. This helps improve the health of underserved patients.

Our unsurpassed in-market expertise and commitment to delivering value, from R&D through to manufacturing, regulatory approvals and commercialisation – means we are there for customers, partners and patients for the long term, every step of the way.
